                    	                        高鐵暑期親子優惠「6～11歲孩童 免費乘車兌換券」歡迎索取。
                    	                    	



本會 高鐵企業會員 暑期親子優惠「6～11歲孩童 免費乘車兌換券」，開放索取中。
 
憑優惠券購買指定車次乘車票之成年旅客，可享同行一名孩童(6～11歲)免費。
限106/07/01～08/31暑假期間搭乘指定車次標準車廂對號座位使用。
 
☞ 提醒您：
1.  使用優惠券時，一名孩童需至少一位成人(包含 敬老票/愛心票/早鳥票/學生票)陪同搭
     乘，且限相同車次及區間；免費孩童不可單獨購票搭乘。
2. 一張優惠券僅限一名孩童免費，不得與其他兌換券合併使用。其他詳細資訊、優惠班
    次，請見高鐵網站/「精選企業獨享 暑期親子優惠」：https://goo.gl/eVCJZX 。
 
☞ 索取方式：請填寫下列表單，每位會員最多索取4張為限，送完為止。
   (秘書處確認索取人確實為本會會員/準會員後，一週內會將優惠券以平信寄出。)
 







                    	                        轉知 APJO Express (Vol. 11, Jun 2017)
                    	                        


                 

[Published twice a month]
The Asia-Pacific Journal of Ophthalmology (APJO) is the official publication of the Asia-Pacific Academy of Ophthalmology (APJO). All APJO articles are freely accessible to members registered on our website.
APJO Express selects top articles from around the world and the APJO. It is circulated to over 50,000 ophthalmologists and visual scientists from the Asia-Pacific region and beyond.
ARTICLE OF THE ISSUE (Vol. 11, Jun 2017)
1. Nanotechnology Applications for Glaucoma
    Cetinel S, Montemagno C. (Asia Pac J Ophthalmol (Phila))
TWO SELECTED ARTICLES FROM AROUND THE WORLD
1. Retinal Pigment Epithelial (RPE) Features Indicative of Neovascular Progression in Age-related
    Macular Degeneration
    Roberts PK, Baumann B, Schlanitz FG, Sacu S, Bolz M, Pircher M, Hagmann M, Hitzenberger CK,
    Schmidt-Erfurth U. (Br J Ophthalmol)
2. Whole-eye Transplantation: a Look into the Past and Vision for the Future
    Bourne D, Li Y, Komatsu C, Miller MR, Davidson EH, He L, Rosner IA, Tang H, Chen W,
    Solari MG, Schuman JS, Washington KM. (Eye (Lond))
TWO SELECTED ARTICLES FROM APJO
1. Intraocular Metastases — A Review
    Konstantinidis L, Damato B. (Asia Pac J Ophthalmol (Phila))
2. Enhancing Medical Student Education by Implementing a Competency-Based Ophthalmology
    Curriculum
    Succar T, McCluskey P, Grigg J. (Asia Pac J Ophthalmol (Phila))
